{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So in that sense, I did not suffer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I maybe moved to Highland Park because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, Highland Park High School is closed on Yom Kippur and Jewish New Year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all the Italians have a free day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I usually-- again, I was not a party-- I was not running with a group, because I was not too keen on the peer pressures.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I always developed very close relationships with individuals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would have one or two very, very close friends with whom I spent most of the time, go to school, come back, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how did I make this friendship?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, of course, this was obviously entirely accidental and synergistic, whatever circumstances were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But indeed, I always had very close friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And probably it was one of the reasons how my life evolved during the war is that I was always able to make a close friend, because I was the only child and maybe I was looking for a substitute of a close family.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tell us what your daily life was like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What would a typical day have been for you as a child?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would, say, go to-- until the age of 10, my father refused for me to go alone to school, because he was-- he was an older when he had me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was very, very frightened of my well-being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so until-- as long as we had nannies, she would take me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came poorer, he would do it himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eventually, the age of 10, 11, I started going to school myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And usually the walk would be probably the distance from here to maybe a little bit further than schools here.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
